{
  "stem": "6900.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She stayed in the barracks looking after the children because Johnny was only four years old.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were young children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, those that they thought could work had to go to work, and those that had young children stayed home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, we worked in a place where we had to cut good leather away from shoes and boots.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Afterwards, we realized who-- [SOBBING] who those boots and shoes belonged to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All our-- at home all went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We weren't allowed to take anything away from it, as I told you before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the SS used to come up and take something out the drawer that you couldn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to come up at night-- when we were in the Jewish quarter-- and see if you were there and-- because some-- a lot of Jewish people went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of Jewish people went into hiding in Amsterdam, those that had money to pay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I heard later-- later that, when the money was up, some of them used to give them up to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they went to the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] What can you say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm scared now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm even scared now what's happening in Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That frightens me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war, my sister and I were in England again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought we'd take-- go into Palestine-- Israel then-- with the two-- with the two boys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my grandmother was still alive, and my family were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not only that, we decided if they had to-- if we went to Israel, they'd have to join the army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they'd had enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we decided to stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'd-- in Belsen?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew nothing about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
